        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="3"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="assets/images/circus_1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>Wild Circus...</h5>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="assets/images/circus_2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>un cirque exceptionnel...</h5>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="assets/images/circus_3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>des num√©ros exceptionnels...</h5>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="assets/images/circus_4.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>...et des artistes exceptionnels.</h5>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="box-home-element">
        <h3 class="title-home mb-5 mt-5 ">Qui sommes nous ?</h3>
        <p class="txt-qsn-home">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque diam ligula, venenatis ut pulvinar id,
            fermentum ac orci. Integer fringilla leo dolor, tincidunt ullamcorper nisi lobortis quis. Nulla et tempus
            eros,
            et interdum enim. Suspendisse in porta quam. Proin id ornare enim, at maximus enim. Nunc id erat sed eros
            vulputate
            semper. Donec vel lacus facilisis nulla hendrerit porttitor a et augue. In vitae faucibus nibh. Curabitur
            sagittis ex eu dui vulputate tincidunt. Mauris mi turpis, finibus quis diam eu, finibus convallis augue. Ut
            sit amet tortor purus. Etiam lacinia ornare augue.
        </p>
    </div>
    <h3 class="title-home">Quelques spectacles</h3>
        {% for performance in performances %}
            <div data-aos="fade-right">
            <div class="card mb-5 mt-5 w-100 h-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                    {% if  performance.image is not null %}
                        <img src="{{ vich_uploader_asset(performance, 'imageFile') }}" class="card-img-top"
                             alt="{{ performance.title }}">
                    {% else %}
                        <img src="assets/images/placeholder.jpg" class="card-img-top"
                             alt="{{ performance.title }}">
                    {% endif %}
                    <div class="card ">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">{{ performance.title }}</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">{{ performance.description }}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
{% endblock %}